  "texts": [
    "The task entails producing a fitting response by leveraging both textual content and a posed question.",
    "The answer, rather than being an exact extraction from the text, is openly generated by the models.",
    "Presently, this task category stands as a predominant focus in the evaluation of LLMs.",
    "DROP (Dua et al, 2019) and QASPER (Dasigi et al, 2021) assess models' reasoning ability to generate open-ended answers.",
    "Answers cannot be directly extracted from the text but require models to search for clues from multiple sources and then perform certain operations."
  ],
